friendsJson.name: Mojo
friendsJson.description: JoJo introduced me to him November 2009. I believe I had met him when he was a calf but I’m not sure. They have brought me for swims with Mo on my left and JoJo on my right. Mo will swim with me when JoJo isn’t around. He had a friend last year and they let me hang with them. He will go to boats and is okay with people swimming around.
